title: Suburgatory Season 3 Complete LOL x264
description:
[2014.07.30] As the title says, this is a season 3 upload of Suburgatory.  I was able to find Season 1 and 2 complete, but noticed a missing season 3 - thus this torrent.

All the episodes were LOL x264 encodes.  I always preferred eztv uploads (no folder structure - just the file), but I know there is *at least* 1 ettv upload where the eztv one didn't show in my search (7/10 ettv gets their upload on TPB before eztv and about the same time as RARbg, so they are my definite fallback!).

I *love* loadstone2k12 uploads because he always seems to include the subs, so I went over to addic7ed.com and downloaded their English subs [regular, not the hearing impaired ones].

I'm doing this upload anonymously, and giving credit where credit is due.  As a regular downloader, I find it *so much easier* to simply download a season or series vs the individual episodes.  Since the other 2 seasons seem to be in good health [lots of seeds] it seemed more appropriate to simply upload the third season.

When they invent "meta-torrents", we could just make a torrent linking other torrents together, then we could have healthy episode, season, and series downloads!

If anybody wonders what I actually mean by a meta-torrent, leave a comment and I'll explain in a follow-up comment.

Otherwise, enjoy season 3 :)
